actionConfiguration.body:
SELECT TopLevelTests.TestName, Tests.Path, TestResults.Result, TestRun.RackID, TestRun.RackTestRun, TestRun.TestDateTimeStop, TestRun.TesterName, TestRun.ATPVersion, TestRun.TestConfigPN, TestRacks.RackPartNumber, TestRacks.RackSerialNumber, TestResults.TestsID, TestResults.TestRunID
FROM TopLevelTests INNER JOIN (TestRacks RIGHT JOIN (Tests INNER JOIN (TestRun INNER JOIN ((LimitSets RIGHT JOIN TestResults ON LimitSets.ID = TestResults.LimitSetID) LEFT JOIN TestReadings ON TestResults.ID = TestReadings.TestResultID) ON TestRun.ID = TestResults.TestRunID) ON Tests.ID = TestResults.[TestsID]) ON TestRacks.ID = TestRun.RackID) ON TopLevelTests.ID = TestRun.TopLevelTestID;
